    "body": "@dfawley, Can you clarify few things for me to understand it better?\r\n\r\n- Which language projections of gRPC uses OpenSSL?\r\n- What do you mean by no \"official\" OpenSSL library? If there is none, which one gRPC uses? \r\n- What issues do you see supporting ENGINE (only for places where you call openSSL)? \r\n  - If any projection is not calling openSSL, we are not asking for its support. \r\n  - We are just asking to expose one supported configuration in openSSL to be also available through gRPC.\r\n- How is your \"credentials.TransportCredentials\" reference different from \"MetadataCredentialsPlugin\" class? Are there any examples of \"TransportCredentials\" that I can fork in the source code?"
  },
